{"name":"sencisho","description":"sencisho is a small http server for your local development","version":"0.3.3","preferGlobal":"true","license":"MIT","repository":"https://github.com/julien/sencisho","keywords":["simple","http","server","livereload"],"main":"./bin/sencisho","bin":{"sencisho":"./bin/sencisho"},"scripts":{"test":"mocha","prepublish":"npm t"},"dependencies":{"gaze":"1.1.2","tiny-lr":"1.0.3"},"devDependencies":{"mocha":"3.3.0"},"engines":{"node":">= 0.10.0"},"homepage":"https://github.com/julien/sencisho","gitHead":"09277851784c0952dfa73b776740ed8ec96ba28d","versions":[{"number":"0.0.1","date":"2013-07-09T11:34:17.317Z"},{"number":"0.0.2","date":"2013-07-29T18:17:03.858Z"},{"number":"0.0.3","date":"2013-07-29T18:20:30.157Z"},{"number":"0.0.4","date":"2013-09-29T12:55:01.465Z"},{"number":"0.0.5","date":"2013-11-01T23:17:24.278Z"},{"number":"0.0.6","date":"2013-11-01T23:40:36.301Z"},{"number":"0.0.7","date":"2013-11-29T23:29:26.940Z"},{"number":"0.0.8","date":"2014-01-19T14:06:22.397Z"},{"number":"0.0.9","date":"2014-02-22T16:56:07.161Z"},{"number":"0.1.0","date":"2014-02-28T10:55:42.141Z"},{"number":"0.1.1","date":"2014-02-28T23:49:05.237Z"},{"number":"0.1.2","date":"2014-03-15T23:08:47.137Z"},{"number":"0.1.3","date":"2014-04-17T14:49:40.834Z"},{"number":"0.1.4","date":"2014-05-12T11:33:34.677Z"},{"number":"0.1.5","date":"2014-07-27T18:15:27.971Z"},{"number":"0.1.6","date":"2014-07-27T18:20:52.215Z"},{"number":"0.1.7","date":"2014-07-27T18:42:51.519Z"},{"number":"0.1.8","date":"2014-07-29T20:20:39.515Z"},{"number":"0.1.9","date":"2014-08-02T20:13:47.464Z"},{"number":"0.2.0","date":"2014-08-02T22:46:00.049Z"},{"number":"0.2.1","date":"2014-08-21T07:32:01.205Z"},{"number":"0.2.2","date":"2014-08-28T20:27:50.141Z"},{"number":"0.2.3","date":"2014-08-31T18:46:23.054Z"},{"number":"0.2.4","date":"2014-10-20T14:32:44.318Z"},{"number":"0.2.5","date":"2017-04-24T12:26:12.194Z"},{"number":"0.2.6","date":"2017-04-24T21:43:13.792Z"},{"number":"0.3.0","date":"2017-04-25T19:43:00.520Z"},{"number":"0.3.1","date":"2017-04-26T18:48:11.235Z"},{"number":"0.3.2","date":"2017-04-26T19:23:16.869Z"},{"number":"0.3.3","date":"2017-04-27T20:04:05.773Z"}],"readme":"# sencisho\r\n\r\n### Description\r\nA simple http server for local development, built on top of Node.js\r\n\r\n### Usage\r\n`npm install -g sencisho`\r\n\r\nFrom the directory you want to serve static files:\r\n\r\n`sencisho [options]`\r\n\r\n#### Options\r\n`--port` `-p` Port number\r\n\r\n`--live` `-l` Enable livereload\r\n\r\n`--browser` `-b` Specify browser\r\n\r\n`--watch` `-w` Additional paths to watch\r\n\r\n`--silent` `-s` Don't automatically open a browser\r\n\r\n`--responses` `-r` Specify a json file containing a response map\r\n\r\n*when using the -r/--responses option, livereload will be enabled*\r\n\r\n\r\n### Examples\r\nStart in default port\r\n\r\n`sencisho`\r\n\r\nStart in specified port\r\n\r\n`sencisho --port 8888` or `sencisho -p 8888`\r\n\r\nEnable livereload\r\n\r\n`sencisho --live` or `sencisho -l`\r\n\r\nOpen in other browser than your system default\r\n\r\n`sencisho --browser opera` or `sencisho -b opera`\r\n\r\nAdd additional paths to the file watcher\r\n\r\n`sencisho --watch js/*.js` or `sencisho -w js/*.js`\r\n\r\nDon't automatically open a browser\r\n\r\n`sencisho --silent` or `sencisho -s`\r\n\r\nSpecify a json file containing a response map\r\n\r\n`sencisho --responses api.json` or `sencisho -r api.json`\r\n\r\nExample:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  \"/api/test\": {\r\n\r\n    \"headers\": {\r\n      \"Content-type\": \"application/json\",\r\n      \"Access-Control-Allow-Origin\": \"*\",\r\n      \"Access-Control-Allow-Headers\": \"X-Requested-With\"\r\n    },\r\n\r\n    \"statusCode\": 200,\r\n\r\n    \"body\": {\r\n      \"name\": \"Something\",\r\n      \"data\": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe only required property is the `body` but you can specify `headers` and a `statusCode`\r\n\r\n\r\nAll at once (may be passed in any order)\r\n\r\n`sencisho -p 8888 -l -b opera -w js/*.js -s -r api.json`\r\n\r\n### Misc\r\n+ What's up with that name?\r\n\r\n  *It's a long story*\r\n\r\n**Authors/Contributors**\r\n\r\n+ *Julien Castelain*  <jcastelain@gmail.com>\r\n+ *Denis Ciccale*     <dciccale@gmail.com>\r\n","starsCount":0,"created":"2013-07-09T11:34:11.874Z","modified":"2017-04-27T20:04:05.773Z","lastPublisher":{"name":"jcastelain","email":"jcastelain@gmail.com"},"owners":[{"name":"jcastelain","email":"jcastelain@gmail.com"}],"other":{"_attachments":{},"_from":".","_id":"sencisho","_nodeVersion":"6.10.2","_npmOperationalInternal":{"host":"packages-18-east.internal.npmjs.com","tmp":"tmp/sencisho-0.3.3.tgz_1493323445104_0.8124141276348382"},"_npmUser":{"name":"jcastelain","email":"jcastelain@gmail.com"},"_npmVersion":"3.10.10","_rev":"7-9abec02a013da10c77e44eb20d39013a","_shasum":"ce933ba55b79dcc2d88d93bbf067696df353227b","author":{"name":"Julien Castelain","email":"jcastelain@gmail.com","url":"http://punkscum.org"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/julien/sencisho/issues"},"contributors":[{"name":"Denis Ciccale","email":"dciccale@gmail.com","url":"http://twitter.com/tdecs"}],"directories":{},"dist-tags":{"latest":"0.3.3"},"dist":{"shasum":"ce933ba55b79dcc2d88d93bbf067696df353227b","tarball":"https://registry.npmjs.org/sencisho/-/sencisho-0.3.3.tgz"},"maintainers":[{"name":"jcastelain","email":"jcastelain@gmail.com"}],"readmeFilename":"README.md","time":{"modified":"2017-04-27T20:04:05.773Z","created":"2013-07-09T11:34:11.874Z","0.0.1":"2013-07-09T11:34:17.317Z","0.0.2":"2013-07-29T18:17:03.858Z","0.0.3":"2013-07-29T18:20:30.157Z","0.0.4":"2013-09-29T12:55:01.465Z","0.0.5":"2013-11-01T23:17:24.278Z","0.0.6":"2013-11-01T23:40:36.301Z","0.0.7":"2013-11-29T23:29:26.940Z","0.0.8":"2014-01-19T14:06:22.397Z","0.0.9":"2014-02-22T16:56:07.161Z","0.1.0":"2014-02-28T10:55:42.141Z","0.1.1":"2014-02-28T23:49:05.237Z","0.1.2":"2014-03-15T23:08:47.137Z","0.1.3":"2014-04-17T14:49:40.834Z","0.1.4":"2014-05-12T11:33:34